#!/usr/bin/env perl
use Lingua::Shakespeare;

The Search for ASCII-Values.

Hamlet, a journalist.
Ophelia, his interviewee.

	Act I: The Interview.

	Scene I: Smalltalk.

[Enter Hamlet and Ophelia]

Hamlet: Listen to your heart. Speak your mind.

Ophelia: You beautiful pretty handsome hero! You are as sweet as the sum of a green tree and yourself. Speak your mind!

[Exeunt]
